}\pard\plain\ltrpar\s2\li1080\fi-360\kerning24\fs48\lang1033\li360 {\pntext\pard\plain\f3\fs56 \'95\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf3\pnfs56{\pntxtb \'95}}{\f2\fs56\cf1 That opens him to Carson\'92s charge that ideally a person would want to know everything about a product. \par 
