}\pard\plain\ltrpar\s3\li1800\fi-360\kerning24\fs40\lang1033\li1080 {\pntext\pard\plain\f3\fs48 \'95\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf3\pnfs48{\pntxtb \'95}}{\f2\fs48\cf1 (b) talking about a reasonable person within a particular industry / sales context. That may obviate the problem with very limited options which Carson raises\par 
