}\pard\plain\ltrpar\s3\li1800\fi-360\kerning24\fs40\lang1033\li1080 {\pntext\pard\plain\f3\fs48 \'95\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf3\pnfs48{\pntxtb \'95}}{\f2\fs48\cf1 \'93By restricting my range of choices so severely, the robber has forced me into a one-sided deal\'94 [11]\par 
